"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/di-yu-shi" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5068955&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610181333" alt="di_yu_shi" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5068955)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/di-yu-shi" >di_yu_shi</a></span></p> 
				 	]]>
